<div class="body" id="fhbody-173580740">
	
		
	

	
		
		<div id="text-173580740" class="p">
			
		 	
				An anonymous reader shares a report:<i> TCS, Infosys, and Wipro, India's top three IT outsourcing firms, have collectively <a href="https://indiadispatch.xyz/2024/04/19/indian-consultancy-firms-tcs-infosys-and-wipro-have-cut-over-60000-jobs-in-a-year/">seen their workforce shrink for the first time in at least 20 years</a>. The trio reported a combined reduction of more than 63,750 employees in the financial year ending March 31, 2024.</i>
		 	
		</div>

		

		

		
			
		
	</div>
